===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|yeerly}}, {{m|enm|yerely}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġēarlīc|t=yearly, of the year, annual}}, equivalent to {{af|en|year|-ly}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|yerelie|t=yearly}}, {{cog|stq|jierelk|t=yearly}}, {{cog|fy|jierliks|t=yearly}}, {{cog|nl|jaarlijks|t=yearly}}, {{cog|de|jährlich|t=yearly}}, {{cog|sv|årlig|t=yearly}}, {{cog|is|árlegur|t=yearly}}.

